{"tid":808580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跪在亞瑟王墓前！《FGO》玩家「飛歐洲找女主角」幫他抽卡","createTime":"2018-09-06T12:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T14:06:50.000Z","uid":120223,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ac9825b7fccdfa613023a114e3c48a9844e0a4","tid":808580,"uid":120223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"為了在手遊裡面抽到夢寐以求的亞瑟王泳裝角色卡，玩家除了拼運氣之外還能怎麼做呢？一名日本FGO玩家居然直接飛到遙遠的英國，跪在傳說中亞瑟王的墓地前求「觀落陰抽卡」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3536/3536392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3536%2F3536392.jpg&h=d258e9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亞瑟王墓地位於英國格拉斯頓伯里修道院（Glastonbury Abbey），寂寥的草皮底下就沉睡著傳說中的圓桌武士領袖，也是Fate系列女主角Saber的原型。但日本網友@hinata5dx遠渡重洋到來，竟然完整重現了Fate動畫的最後一幕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3536/3536388.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3536%2F3536388.jpg&h=54e3e17f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3536/3536389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3536%2F3536389.jpg&h=9849e1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝聖之旅的重點果然還是手遊角色卡，日本網友隨即跪在亞瑟王的墓前，叨唸著「讓我抽中女主角的泳裝卡吧～～」但現實是殘酷的，當場花了日幣7萬元（約台幣2萬元）抽卡的結果還是槓龜。<br />\n<br />\n▼日本網友hinata5DX表示，在墓前跪著花7萬日幣，還是沒抽到泳裝亞瑟王角色卡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3536/3536391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3536%2F3536391.jpg&h=5cd7ee17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息回傳日本國內，立馬引起了FGO玩家間的佩服讚嘆與安慰，紛紛建議這位遠赴英國的重度玩家「沒抽到卡沒關係，放鬆心情去逛大英博物館吧」、「別難過，當作旅行的插曲吧」「亞瑟王如果知道自己被變性，還被套上泳裝，只會想出土爆揍你一頓」。<br />\n<br />\n能飛到歐洲求當歐洲人的玩家，肯定是不缺錢的，但面對現實，修道院裡的墓地只是紀念性質，並沒有埋藏屍骨，而且真實中的亞瑟王...是個男人啊。"},{"pid":"58b6179deae77ead80c38baa4b6d4b56ab6ff78f","tid":808580,"uid":120223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/38218?from=fb_lemon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F38218%3Ffrom%3Dfb_lemon&d=%2FkFLIGE7jG3W9RG5LudnmdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=57baee18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/38218?from=fb_lemon</a>"},{"pid":"55a9648b2ab252b1dd2a1cc55e538bc3c9fcfce4","tid":808580,"uid":77196,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/06/202713_49371a505a27d885e5c493d26fb2c992.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F202713_49371a505a27d885e5c493d26fb2c992.png&h=3da675f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4af33d0824039ada625b266ab024dfc3105aefc2","tid":808580,"uid":60366,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"死毒撚好玩唔玩，去人地個墳到玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec10a3d9eed49b4c92d61dc0d3b2ef95023933d","tid":808580,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"佢7萬yen都唔中<br />\n好誇張姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8224a76c49abdf24db5f8685c57b5c066ecd7aae","tid":808580,"uid":113000,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4af33d0824039ada625b266ab024dfc3105aefc2","tid":808580,"uid":60366,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"死毒撚好玩唔玩，去人地個墳到玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"咪話個到無骨囉"},{"pid":"f9c2e5c3da3d89d23dc436c6095ebb44556ff912","tid":808580,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bec10a3d9eed49b4c92d61dc0d3b2ef95023933d","tid":808580,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"佢7萬yen都唔